question: Please provide names of the patients that are linked with the organization ROYAL OF FAIRHAVEN NURSING CENTER.
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  p.FIRST || ' ' || p.LAST AS PatientName
FROM patients AS p
INNER JOIN encounters AS e
  ON p.Id = e.PATIENT
INNER JOIN organizations AS o
  ON e.ORGANIZATION = o.Id
WHERE
  o.NAME = 'ROYAL OF FAIRHAVEN NURSING CENTER';
```

question: Can you tell me when the observation Platelet distribution width [Entitic volume] in Blood by Automated count was recorded?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  o.NAME AS OrganizationName,
  p.FIRST AS PatientFirstName,
  p.LAST AS PatientLastName,
  DATE AS DateOfObservation,
  o.ADDRESS AS OrganizationAddress,
  o.CITY AS OrganizationCity,
  o.STATE AS OrganizationState,
  o.ZIP AS OrganizationZip
FROM organizations AS o
JOIN encounters AS e
  ON o.Id = e.ORGANIZATION
JOIN patients AS p
  ON e.PATIENT = p.Id
JOIN observations AS obs
  ON e.Id = obs.ENCOUNTER
WHERE
  obs.CODE = 77720005 AND obs.CATEGORY = 'Laboratory'
ORDER BY
  DateOfObservation DESC
LIMIT 5;
```

question: What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Tree pollen (substance)?
answers:
```sql
WITH TreePollenPatients AS (
  SELECT
    DISTINCT
    p.Patient
  FROM Procedures AS p
  JOIN Encounters AS e
    ON p.Encounter = e.Id
  JOIN Patients AS patient
    ON e.Patient = patient.Id
  JOIN Medications AS m
    ON patient.Id = m.Patient
  WHERE
    m.Description = 'Tree pollen extract'
)
SELECT
  COUNT(p.CODE) AS NumProcedures,
  p.Description
FROM Procedures AS p
JOIN Encounters AS e
  ON p.Encounter = e.Id
WHERE
  e.Patient IN (
    SELECT
      Patient
    FROM TreePollenPatients
  )
GROUP BY
  p.Description
ORDER BY
  NumProcedures DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

```sql
            SELECT
```
```sql
              Procedures.Code
            FROM Procedures
            JOIN Encounters
              ON Procedures.Encounter = Encounters.Id
            JOIN Payers
              ON Encounters.Payer = Payers.Id

      )
  );
```

question: Please provide me the number of procedures covered by the payer Medicaid.

```sql
FROM Procedures AS p
```

question: How long does Levora 0.15/30 28 Day Pack effect last?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  DISTINCT
  CASE
    WHEN to_char(MAX(stop), 'YYYY-MM-DD') = to_char(DATE('now'), 'YYYY-MM-DD')
    THEN CASE
      WHEN ABS(strftime('%J', 'now') - strftime('%J', stop)) > 365
      THEN (
        strftime('%Y', 'now') - strftime('%Y', stop)
      )
      || ' years ago'
      ELSE (
        strftime('%J', 'now') - strftime('%J', stop)
      )
      || ' days'
    END
    ELSE CASE
      WHEN ABS(strftime('%m', 'now') - strftime('%m', stop)) > 1
      THEN CASE
        WHEN ABS(strftime('%m', 'now') - strftime('%m', stop)) > 12
        THEN (
          strftime('%Y', 'now') - strftime('%Y', stop)
        )
        || ' years ago'
        ELSE (
          strftime('%m', 'now') - strftime('%m', stop)
        )
        || ' months ago'
      END
      ELSE CASE
        WHEN ABS(strftime('%d', 'now') - strftime('%d', stop)) > 28
        THEN (
          strftime('%d', 'now') - strftime('%d', stop)
        )
        || ' days ago'
        ELSE CASE
          WHEN ABS(strftime('%H', 'now') - strftime('%H', stop)) > 8
          THEN (
            strftime('%H', 'now') - strftime('%H', stop)
          )
          || ' hr ago'
          ELSE CASE
            WHEN ABS(strftime('%M', 'now') - strftime('%M', stop)) < 1
            THEN 'less than 1 min ago'
            ELSE (
              strftime('%M', 'now') - strftime('%M', stop)
            )
            || ' min ago'
          END
        END
      END
    END
  END AS how_long_ago
FROM medications
WHERE
  code = (
```

question: What are the potential side effects and drug interactions associated with the medication Alendronic acid 10 MG Oral Tablet?

```sql

  ad.DESCRIPTION AS Side_Effects,
  ad.REASONDESCRIPTION AS Side_Effects_Reason,

FROM Medications AS m
JOIN Adverse_Drug_Reactions AS ad

JOIN Drug_Interactions AS di

JOIN Payers AS p
  ON m.PAYER = p.Id
JOIN Patient_Transitions AS pt
  ON m.PATIENT = pt.PATIENT
WHERE
  m.DESCRIPTION = 'Alendronic acid 10 MG Oral Tablet';
```

question: What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Animal dander (substance)?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  Procedures.CODE, /* Procedure Code */
  Procedures.DESCRIPTION, /* Procedure Description */
  COUNT(*) AS TotalProcedures /* Total Number of Procedures Performed for Patients with Animal Dander */
FROM Procedures
JOIN Encounters
  ON Procedures.ENCOUNTER = Encounters.Id
JOIN patients
  ON patients.id = Encounters.PATIENT
JOIN allergies /* Join on Allergies where the substance is Animal Dander */
  ON patients.id = allergies.PATIENT
  AND allergies.DESCRIPTION = 'Animal dander'
WHERE
  Procedures.START > allergies.START /* Procedure should have started after the allergy onset */
GROUP BY
  Procedures.CODE,
  Procedures.DESCRIPTION
ORDER BY
  TotalProcedures DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

question: Which illness is most common in warmer climates?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  d.DESCRIPTION
FROM conditions AS c
JOIN patients AS p
  ON c.PATIENT = p.ID
JOIN organizations AS o
  ON p.ADDRESS = o.ADDRESS
WHERE
  o.LAT IN (
    SELECT
      LAT
    FROM organizations
    WHERE
      LON IN (
        SELECT
          LON
        FROM organizations
        WHERE
          CITY IN (
            SELECT
              CITY
            FROM organizations
            WHERE
              TEMPERATURE > 70
          )
      )
  )
GROUP BY
  d.CODE
ORDER BY
  COUNT(d.CODE) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

question: What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Mold (organism)?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  p.FIRST,
  p.LAST,
  p.GENDER,
  p.RACE,
  p.ETHNICITY,
  p.BIRTHDATE,
  p.STATE,
  p.CITY,
  p.HEALTHCARE_EXPENSES,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT pr.DESCRIPTION)
FROM patients AS p
JOIN encounters AS e
  ON p.Id = e.PATIENT
JOIN procedures AS pr
  ON e.Id = pr.ENCOUNTER
WHERE
  pr.CODE IN (
    SELECT
      CODE
    FROM allergies
    WHERE
      DESCRIPTION LIKE '%Mold%'
  )
GROUP BY
  p.Id
HAVING
  COUNT(DISTINCT pr.DESCRIPTION) > 1
ORDER BY
  COUNT(DISTINCT pr.DESCRIPTION) DESC;
```

question: Please provide me reasons for performing the procedure Movement therapy (regime/therapy).
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  DISTINCT
  r.DESCRIPTION AS reason
FROM conditions AS c
JOIN encounters AS e
  ON c.PATIENT = e.PATIENT
JOIN procedures AS p
  ON c.ENCOUNTER = p.ENCOUNTER
JOIN patients AS pa
  ON e.PATIENT = pa.id
JOIN payers AS py
  ON e.PAYER = py.ID
JOIN reasons AS r
  ON c.CODE = r.REASONCODE
WHERE
  p.DESCRIPTION LIKE '%Movement therapy (regime/therapy)%';
```

question: What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Allergy to substance (finding)?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  MAX(DESK.COST) AS MOST_PROMISING_PROCEDURE
FROM (
  SELECT
    DISTINCT
    PROC.CODE,
    PROC.DESCRIPTION,
    CNDS.DESCRIPTION AS FINDING,
    PROC.BASE_COST AS COST
  FROM PROCEDURES AS PROC
  JOIN ENCOUNTERS AS ENTRS
    ON PROC.ENCOUNTER = ENTRS.ID
  JOIN PATIENTS AS PTS
    ON ENTRS.PATIENT = PTS.ID
  JOIN CONDITIONS AS CNDS
    ON CNDS.ENCOUNTER = ENTRS.ID
  WHERE
    PTS.ID = '9475a286-6af4-438f-a08b-f093326f2fe5' AND CNDS.DESCRIPTION = 'Allergy to substance'
) AS DESK;
```

question: In what climate does Allergy to substance (finding) occur in most?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  t1.description AS finding,
  p.city,
  p.state,
  p.country,
  COUNT(p.id) AS cnt
FROM allergies AS t1
JOIN conditions AS t2
  ON t1.patient = t2.patient AND t1.encounter = t2.encounter AND t1.code = t2.code
JOIN patients AS p
  ON t1.patient = p.id
WHERE
  t2.description LIKE '%Allergy to substance%'
GROUP BY
  1,
  2,
  3,
  4
ORDER BY
  cnt DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

question: What is the most promising procedure for a patient with Allergy to substance (finding)?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  procedures.CODE,
  COUNT(procedures.CODE) AS procedure_count
FROM allergies
LEFT JOIN encounters
  ON allergies.PATIENT = encounters.PATIENT
LEFT JOIN procedures
  ON encounters.ID = procedures.ENCOUNTER
WHERE
  allergies.CODE = 639.9 AND procedures.STOP IS NULL
GROUP BY
  procedures.CODE
ORDER BY
  procedure_count DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

question: What is the successrate of medication Simvastatin 10 MG Oral Tablet?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN COUNT(DISTINCT p.Id) IS NULL
    THEN 0
    ELSE ROUND((
      COUNT(DISTINCT p.Id) * 1.0 / COUNT(DISTINCT m.Id)
    ) * 100, 2)
  END AS successrate
FROM patients AS p
JOIN medications AS m
  ON p.Id = m.PATIENT
WHERE
  p.Id IN (
    SELECT DISTINCT
      PATIENT
    FROM medications
    WHERE
      DESCRIPTION LIKE '%Simvastatin 10 MG Oral Tablet%' AND CODE IN (
        SELECT DISTINCT
          CODE
        FROM medications
        WHERE
          CODE IN (
            SELECT DISTINCT
              CODE
            FROM medications
            WHERE
              BASE_COST > 0 AND PAYER_COVERAGE > 0
          )
      )
  );
```

question: Please provide me the udi code related to the device Home nebulizer (physical object).

question: What is the classification of Wheat (substance)?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  DESCRIPTION
FROM allergies
WHERE
  CODE IN (
    SELECT
      CODE
    FROM allergies
    WHERE
      DESCRIPTION = 'Wheat'
  );
```

question: What is the total number of months being a member for the payer with ID b046940f-1664-3047-bca7-dfa76be352a4?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  SUM(pt.MEMBER_MONTHS) AS total_member_months
FROM payers AS pt
WHERE
  pt.Id = 'b046940f-1664-3047-bca7-dfa76be352a4';
```

question: Please provide me the number of medications covered by the payer with the ID 8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce.
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  COUNT(DISTINCT M.CODE) AS Number_Of_Covered_Medications
FROM medications AS M
JOIN payers AS P
  ON M.PAYER = P.ID
WHERE
  P.ID = '8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce';
```

question: Can you tell me when the observation Body mass index (BMI) [Ratio] was recorded?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  o.DATE
FROM observations AS o
JOIN patients AS p
  ON o.PATIENT = p.Id
WHERE
  o.CODE = '8302-2' AND o.TYPE = 'numeric';
```

question: Please provide me the patients who have received the immunization with code 140.
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  DISTINCT
  p.Id AS Patient_ID,
  p.FIRST AS Patient_First_Name,
  p.LAST AS Patient_Last_Name
FROM patients AS p
JOIN immunizations AS i
  ON p.Id = i.Patient
WHERE
  i.CODE = 140;
```

question: Who is the patient associated with the claim cca769d0-09e0-72f9-23aa-e6ddb2200792?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  p.FIRST,
  p.LAST
FROM claims AS c
JOIN patients AS p
  ON c.patientID = p.id
WHERE
  c.id = 'cca769d0-09e0-72f9-23aa-e6ddb2200792';
```

question: Please provide me the number of immunizations uncovered by the payer Cigna Health.
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  COUNT(DISTINCT ei.CODE) AS count_uncovered_immunizations
FROM immunizations AS ei
JOIN encounters AS e
  ON e.ID = ei.ENCOUNTER
JOIN payers AS p
  ON p.ID = e.PAYER
WHERE
  p.NAME = 'Cigna Health';
```

question: Who has been treated with the procedure Depression screening using Patient Health Questionnaire Nine Item score (procedure)?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  DISTINCT
  patients.first,
  patients.last
FROM patients
JOIN encounters
  ON patients.id = encounters.patient
JOIN procedures
  ON encounters.id = procedures.encounter
WHERE
  procedures.code = 30968;
```

question: What is the state of residence of the patient named Oralia106 Lockman863?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  s.STATE
FROM patients AS p
JOIN organizations AS o
  ON p.ADDRESS = o.ADDRESS
JOIN cities AS c
  ON p.CITY = c.CITY
JOIN states AS s
  ON p.STATE = s.STATE
WHERE
  p.FIRST || ' ' || p.LAST = 'Oralia106 Lockman863';
```

question: What is the specialty of the provider with the ID bde3a54e-2e9e-3c99-b4e3-1d9cdbccb10d?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  s.SPECIALITY
FROM PROVIDERS AS p
JOIN ORGANIZATIONS AS o
  ON p.ORGANIZATION = o.Id
JOIN SPECIALITY AS s
  ON p.SPECIALITY = s.Id
WHERE
  p.Id = 'bde3a54e-2e9e-3c99-b4e3-1d9cdbccb10d';
```
